STATE
v.
Jacob CRAIN. No. 251P08-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 11, 2008. Catherine F. Jordan, Assistant Attorney General, Jerry Wilson, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 1st day of December 2008 by Defendant to Dismiss on Grounds of "Excess of Jurisdiction":

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 11th day of December 2008."
